title: UFYB 6: How to Get Sh*t Done
itunes:title: How to Get Sh*t Done
description:
Today, we're talking about how you can get more things done in a given time and avoid unnecessary anxiety in the process.We also take a look at the reasons why you’re not getting as much done as you want or need to.

Join us as I explain how you can create a clear system and organize your work and personal life to have more time, save mental energy, and eliminate overwhelm.

Get full show notes and more information here: http://bit.ly/2BtRqBA
